	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=127934><span id=Scholar>Dadalan</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>18 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>It's a charm based augmentation. It has nothing to do with your current Adventurer's Stone... but rather your faction with the Wayfarers. You could destroy it, get a new one, destroy it, get a new one and re-apply it to your charm and get the same increase in stats.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
