	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=127934><span id=Scholar>Dadalan</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>18 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Depends on the augmentation. The basic items on the adventure merchants that you can see before you do any adventures are all Charm augmentations. They say &quot;will give you &lt;effect&gt; when you are in a LDoN zone&quot;, but that is how charms are... only work under certain conditions. All other augmentations that are for other items (armor, weapons, etc.) are straight up upgrades to your items. So if you add 5 STR to your BP then no matter where you are (LDoN or otherwise) you will have 5 more STR when you wear that BP.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
